Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.29,0:22:38.75,Dial_CH,,0,600,0,,說到通知表很煩來著
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.02,0:22:42.22,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,哈欠
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.98,0:23:29.54,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,曲睡著了
