Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:41.71,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(360,360)}若何時笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:45.21,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(360,360)}若何時迴歸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:48.71,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(360,360)}就將所有拘束都卸下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:02:01.68,OP_CHT,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(360,360)}我守護的心靈是你所給予的
